$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror-mode-ja.text: This plugin adds Syntax Highlighting for Javascript tiddlers (application/javascript) to the [[CodeMirror|http://codemirror.net]] text editor. It needs the latest [[CodeMirror plugin|$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror]] to be installed
